<ab><lb n="1"/> <w lemma="ὁ"><unclear>ἡ</unclear></w> <w lemma="σορός"><unclear>σορό</unclear>ς</w> <w lemma="εἰμί">ἐστιν</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w> <w lemma="περί">περὶ</w> <w lemma="αὐτός">αὐτὴν</w> <w lemma="πλάτος"><unclear>π</unclear>λά<unclear>τ</unclear>ος</w> <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Ποπλία">Ποπλίας</name> <name nymRef="#Καλβισία">Κα<unclear>λ</unclear>βισίας</name></persName> 
   <lb n="2"/> <note xml:lang=""/> <w lemma="ζάω">ΩΖ <milestone unit="block"/> ΣΙΝ</w> 
   <lb n="3"/> <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Περιτιανή">Περιτιανῆς</name></persName> <w lemma="ὁ">τῆς</w> <w lemma="ἔγγονος">ἐγγόνου</w> <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Ἰουλιανός">Ἰουλιανοῦ</name></persName> <w lemma="ὁ">τῆς</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> </ab>
</div>
         <div type="apparatus">
           <listApp>
            <app loc="1"><note><foreign xml:lang="grc">πλατός</foreign> is generally taken to be used as an equivalent of <foreign xml:lang="grc">πλατάς</foreign>, a platform for a tomb.</note></app>
            <app loc="2"><note>clearly misinscribed for ζῶσιν.</note></app>
            <app loc="3"><note>the text was presumably completed on the chest of the sarcophagus.</note></app>
           </listApp>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p> i. The sarcophagus and the surrounding platform belongs to Publia Calvisia Peritiane, the grandaughter of Iulianos; she also 
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
            <p>ii. They live.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
       <!--      <p>Line 2 is commonly taken to indicate that the owners of the tomb were still alive, and the formula used here for peritiane would accord with that possibility, although it has been thought by some that continued existence after burial is indicated. P. Calvisia Peritiane is not otherwise attested at present. It is unusual that she is identified in the first instance by reference to a gradfather. He too is not identifiable at present.</p>
         --> </div>
